title: Ep. 646 - Ten Years In Federal Prison For A Meme
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, the FBI is now arresting Trump supporters for posting memes. Also Five Headlines including the drama on the stock market and Harriet Tubman replacing Andrew Jackson on the twenty dollar bill. And in our Daily Cancellation, we’ll discuss the Instagram baby expert who was doxxed, harassed, and boycotted after it was revealed that she had committed the crime of donating to Donald Trump.
